
Abunuabunu yɛ nkwan a won a wɔn wɔ Bono ne Ahafo Mantam mu wɔ Ghana no yɛ. Wɔde mankani ahaban a wɔfrɛ no kontomire ne atosodeɛ ahorɔw te sɛ (Tomantose, nnwa, adwen anaa nsuomnam, gyene, mako, kwahu nsosuaa ne nkyene.

== ɔkwan a wɔfa so kyɛ ==
Abunuabunu  yɛ aduane eho nnya na wɔ amanfoɔ wɔn wɔ Kumasi. Wɔde nkwan yi di fufuo anaa banku nanso, wobetumi de adi aduane biara a wo pe.

== Ayɛdeɛ ==

* Nnwa
* Adwene
* Mmire
* Koobi 
* 10-15  Mankani Ahaban (Kontomire)
* kwansesaawa 
* Atosodeɛ (gyene, Makobunu , tomantose, kakaduro, garlic)
* Nkyene
* andwene a w'ahow
* dawawa

== Sɛnea wɔyɛ no ==

* Fa ankaatwɛdeɛ hohoro nnwa no
* Twitwa mmire ne koobi no mu nketenkete gu dadesɛn keseɛ mu
* Fa nnwa no gu so
* Fa nkyene ne gyene,kakduro ne garlic a w'anyam afra no punu wɔ dadesɛn no mu
* Hohoro tomantose ne gyene foforo gu so, na afei kata dadesɛn no so
* Tete kontomire nnua no, na hohoro kontomire no yiyie
* Fa nkontomire no gu dadesɛn mu, na mako, nusuo nekwansesaawa gu so, kata so ma no nhuru beye sima 5 -8 .
* Yiyi tomantose ne gyene no na hwɛ sɛ aben anaa, nyam ne nyinaa fra.
* Fa sɔnyɛ sɔne so gu nkwan no mu
* Hohoro adwene a w'ahow no na fa to nkwan no mu.
* Kata so ma no nhuru bɛyɛ sima 5
* Twitwa Ahaban no, Mako ne kwansesaawa ma ɛnfe fekoko na fa gu nkwan no mu.
* Fa nsuo kakra gu mu sɛ wohwɛ na api dodo 
* Ka hwɛ na fa nkyene gu mu
* Ma ogya no mmara fɔm na ma nkwan no nsi so bɛyɛ sima 6 kosi du natam
* Fa di fufuo, mmotuo anaa bibiara a wo pɛ 

